cbir.image

Class ImageContainer

  • java.lang.Object
    • cbir.image.ImageContainer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class ImageContainer
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    A class which implements an image (jpeg...). An image has a filename, a list of descriptors, lists of positive and negative images marked during RF and an optional label.
    Author:
    Matej Stanic, Chris Wendler
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
